1
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,200
The tea tastes good.

2
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,200
Qianqiao,

3
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,240
these guards can leave.

4
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,240
Even if Mo Huaiyang is an idiot,

5
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:23,040
he wouldn't hide the Glazed Armor here.

6
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,840
These guards are just
pretending to work hard.

7
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,120
Yes.

8
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,840
Let's go.

9
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,320
Your Majesty,

10
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,360
how long should we wait?

11
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,200
How about

12
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,760
letting me set a fire

13
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:52,000
to force them out?

14
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,080
What's the rush?

15
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,280
Mo Huaiyang can't run away forever.

16
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:02,000
As long as his disciples are here,

17
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:05,040
he will come eventually.

18
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,640
But Your Majesty, accidents might happen.

19
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:10,960
We brought
so many Drug Men here this time.

20
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:13,320
If one of them

21
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,000
gets away,

22
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,080
things may go south.

23
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,000
What if

24
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,560
Mo Huaiyang brings help?

25
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,040
In that case,

26
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,480
we will kill

27
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,120
anyone who stands in the way.

28
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,600
Have some food.

29
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,200
Idiot,

30
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:19,000
don't you have anything to ask?

31
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,000
I--

32
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,400
I--

33
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,120
I do.

34
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,840
Gu Xiang,

35
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,640
who are you exactly?

36
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,640
Why don't you ask me

37
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:49,280
in front of Master Fan and your senior?

38
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:54,480
If I did, then,

39
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,320
what should you do?

40
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,520
Do you care about me that much?

41
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,360
Of course!

42
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,960
I've already promised Mr. Wen.

43
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:07,680
That Wen Kexing.

44
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,480
How can he be the chief
of the Ghost Valley?

45
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,640
He--

46
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,240
he has a close relationship
with Mr. Zhou and Chengling.

47
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:22,320
Yes. He's Hero Zhen's descendant, right?

48
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,120
Gu Xiang,

49
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:29,040
are there any misunderstandings?

50
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:34,480
Mr. Wen was framed by others,

51
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,280
so he did that on purpose,

52
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,080
didn't he?

53
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,400
It doesn't matter

54
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,560
whether it's true or not.

55
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,160
If it's a misunderstanding,

56
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,600
I will prove your innocence,

57
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,560
even if it costs me my life.

58
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,120
What if it's true?

59
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,440
What if I'm a lone ghost
from Mount Qingya,

60
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,640
coming to the human world by accident,

61
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,880
then meeting you

62
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,840
and deceiving you?

63
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,800
Weining,

64
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,680
will you kill me?

65
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,920
In the place where I grew up,

66
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,000
there were people
always killing each other.

67
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,880
Even if there's only a 1% chance,

68
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,240
it's better to kill the wrong guy
instead of letting him go.

69
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,240
If I don't do that,

70
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,960
I wouldn't be able to be alive.

71
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,120
If--

72
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,840
if you were a spy sent by the Ghost Valley

73
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,280
and deceived me on purpose

74
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,840
to get into the Gentle Wind Sword Sect

75
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,480
and bring your allies here,

76
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,400
so that you could kill us

77
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,080
and destroy our sect,

78
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,920
I would kill you without a doubt.

79
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,760
All right then.

80
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,040
But Gu Xiang,

81
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,320
do you know?

82
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,280
I've sworn an oath.

83
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:33,120
I, Cao Weining, will never fail you

84
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,920
in my life, not for once.

85
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,280
But in this matter,

86
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:44,480
I'm not sure if that counts
as failing you.

87
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,920
But rest assured, Gu Xiang.

88
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,160
If I kill you,

89
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,720
I will kill myself right after that.

90
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:58,320
I will go with you to the netherworld.

91
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,800
Let's reincarnate together, hand in hand.

92
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,360
Gu Xiang,

93
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,360
please believe me.

94
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:07,960
In the next life,

95
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,280
I'll grow up with you

96
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:14,000
so you won't follow any bad examples
or go through any hardship.

97
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:21,560
But Gu Xiang, I don't think you are a spy.

98
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,720
I know you are a good girl.

99
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,000
So Gu Xiang, please tell me,

100
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,640
what's going on?

101
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,280
If I tell you,

102
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,520
will you believe me?

103
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,760
I will.

104
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,200
Gu Xiang.

105
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,680
Gu Xiang.

106
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,840
Gu Xiang, don't cry.

107
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,440
I believe you. I do.

108
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,680
As long as you tell me.

109
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:11,080
Gu Xiang, please don't cry.

110
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,760
I'll tell you.

111
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,000
All of it.

112
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,440
Come here.

113
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:19,840
Sit down. Let me tell you.

114
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,040
My master's name is Wen Kexing.

115
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,640
He is the chief of the Ghost Valley.

116
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,840
But he has decided to be a good person.

117
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:26,920
No, that's not right.

118
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,480
He is a good person.

119
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,760
He just wanted to seek revenge

120
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,800
and he didn't need the Glazed Armor.

121
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,840
He won't be the enemy of your sect either.

122
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:36,560
Gu Xiang, slow down. I can't follow you.

123
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:40,680
All right.
Then, I'll start from the beginning.

124
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,960
Before I grew up in the Ghost Valley.

125
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,880
Since--

126
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:51,160
Since I began to remember things,
I had been in the Ghost Valley.

127
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,560
Back then,

128
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:55,000
my master was only a teenager.

129
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,720
He was serving the old chief.

130
00:09:57,800 --> 00:10:01,160
He said I was picked up from the waters,

131
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,680
so my name is Gu Xiang.

132
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,720
I believed it for years.

133
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,400
But later, I realized it was a lie.

134
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,280
The old chief kidnapped some children

135
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,960
to help him practice some evil skill.

136
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,440
All the other children had died,
except for me.

137
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:14,280
My master begged the old chief

138
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,280
to keep me as a living toy,

139
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:18,200
so I survived.

140
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:21,880
Children who grew up in the Ghost Valley

141
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,760
consider killing as natural as breathing.

142
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,520
Everybody thought

143
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:28,480
the law of this world is that
only the powerful can survive.

144
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:31,360
But my master told me
that was not the case.

145
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,320
There was a place called
the "human world."

146
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:36,440
I was just a little kid
who entered the Ghost Valley by mistake.

147
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:39,200
He said that
he would send me back one day.

148
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:41,120
Not until I grew up did I realize

149
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:43,560
that my master had protected me
so many times.

150
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,440
One day,

151
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:49,040
my master started a riot
in the Ghost Valley.

152
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,640
He killed the old chief
and took the throne.

153
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,240
In the following years,

154
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,840
-Master killed every one
-Chief!

155
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:56,240
of the former Ten Devils

156
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,560
and replaced them with new ones.

157
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:00,120
"Lunatic Wen" became his nickname.

158
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:02,600
Back then, I didn't take it seriously.

159
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:04,360
My master became the new chief.

160
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,720
I was thrilled
because I could do whatever I wanted.

161
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,600
Until one day,

162
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:11,600
my master said
he had finally completed his plan

163
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,440
and he would take me to the human world.

164
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,640
Order all 3,000 ghosts in Mount Qingya.

165
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,920
From now on,

166
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,840
I want everyone to go out

167
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:28,240
and kill the traitor.

168
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,640
Whoever can get

169
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,520
the Glazed Armor back for me

170
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:38,560
will be the head of Ten Devils!

171
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,880
So you went out

172
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,160
to kill Hanged Ghost
and get the Glazed Armor.

173
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,880
You idiot. I explained it for so long.

174
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:48,320
This is just an excuse.
Master only wanted to take revenge.

175
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,960
After the Zhen couple died,

176
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:54,560
Mr. Wen was kidnapped and
brought back to the Ghost Valley, right?

177
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:57,800
No wonder when he met Hero Shen Shen,

178
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,080
he looked so devastated.

179
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:06,000
I'm sorry. You've been through a lot.

180
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,400
Wait.

181
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:14,000
The ghosts killed his parents,

182
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,800
yet kept him around.

183
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:18,680
Aren't they afraid
that he will take revenge on them later?

184
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,280
Whoever enters the Valley

185
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:24,160
has to drink a decoction
named the Soup of Oblivion.

186
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:27,640
After consuming it, they'll forget
the deep obsession of their life.

187
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,760
The old chief thought

188
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,880
my master had forgotten about his parents.

189
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,160
But he didn't.

190
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,560
He has a strong mind.

191
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,920
He buried his hatred deep in his heart.

192
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,040
Master Wen.

193
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:52,240
Master Wen!

194
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,400
Finally, you are awake.

195
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:56,600
As you were unconscious for several days,
I was scared to death.

196
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,280
Right.

197
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:01,320
Master Wen, this is--

198
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,600
Master Wen,

199
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,840
I'm Jing Beiyuan,
the seventh child of my generation.

200
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,760
This is Nanjiang's Great Shaman.

201
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,840
You are so kind to come all the way here

202
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,280
to help us out.

203
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,400
Please accept my bow.

204
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,680
Master Wen,

205
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:16,240
there's no need for that.

206
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:19,480
I owe Zishu my life.

207
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:22,160
Beiyuan, we can catch up later.

208
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,600
Master Wen has been unconscious for days.

209
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:25,880
We have lost our advantage.

210
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:29,080
Perhaps Lord Zhou
has been sent to Jin now.

211
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:32,120
Our priority is to save him.

212
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,680
But the Window of Heaven
is heavily guarded.

213
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:37,240
We may not be strong enough to make it.

214
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:41,120
Our team from Nanjiang

215
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,040
only brought a few bodyguards along.

216
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,800
It's too late to call for backup.

217
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,440
What happened to Zhou Xu?

218
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:56,560
WHITE CLOTH

219
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,760
WHITE CLOTH

220
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,160
Master Zhou, please.

221
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,320
I've already taken the Muscle Relaxants.

222
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,840
This is unnecessary.

223
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,160
Please forgive us.

224
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:57,560
Let's go.

225
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:23,280
WHITE CLOTH

226
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:27,800
WHITE CLOTH

227
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:39,840
PLEASANT VIRTUE

228
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,200
Your Highness.

229
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:49,880
All right.

230
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,760
Pengju, thank you.

231
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:54,800
Go and get some rest.

232
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:57,480
-Your Highness.
-You may go.

233
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,760
Yes, Your Highness.

234
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:09,840
Let's go.

235
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:21,720
Zishu,

236
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:24,680
why don't you come in?

237
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:34,680
PLEASANT VIRTUE

238
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:36,160
You are quite something.

239
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:39,360
I have to come to you, don't I?

240
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:46,640
Your Highness.

241
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:48,760
The homeland has been destroyed.

242
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:52,640
You don't have to keep me

243
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,760
or this sword.

244
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,520
It's so sharp.

245
00:17:07,080 --> 00:17:09,120
It should go back to whom it belongs.

246
00:17:12,560 --> 00:17:13,760
Follow me.

247
00:17:13,840 --> 00:17:15,840
I've prepared you a jar of fine wine.

248
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:25,920
WHITE CLOTH

249
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:49,320
It's the wine in Qingluan's courtyard.

250
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:09,160
As the years have gone by,

251
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:11,520
there is not much left.

252
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:20,000
We made a promise back then, right?

253
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:21,560
Ten years later,

254
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:24,240
with the same people

255
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:25,840
in that same yard.

256
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:28,280
We will open it and drink it up.

257
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,520
Same people?

258
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,920
They've all left.

259
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,920
Yunxing went far away to the borderland.

260
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,360
Qingluan committed suicide.

261
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,680
Prince Qi was poisoned by you.

262
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:47,520
Jiuxiao died in Lucheng in a battle.

263
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:50,920
Among those who were in that yard,

264
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:53,760
only you and I are here now.

265
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,520
Hundreds of times

266
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:03,520
when I fell into dreams at midnight,

267
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:06,800
I went back
to that flower-blooming courtyard.

268
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:09,920
Beiyuan was playing his guqin.

269
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,240
Jiuxiao was playing his xiao.

270
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:14,560
Yunxing was brandishing his sword
and Qingluan was composing songs.

271
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:18,280
As I turned back,

272
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:22,840
you were standing by my side.

273
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:27,480
You were right.

274
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,000
Zishu.

275
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:33,320
All our friends have left.

276
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,400
Now, there are only both of us.

277
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:37,760
The bond between us

278
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:41,720
is an entanglement of favor
and resentment.

279
00:19:42,280 --> 00:19:44,880
I don't want
to hold on to the past anymore.

