00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:13,680
PLEASANT VIRTUE

286
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,280
Good wine.

287
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,400
Time is essential to wine

288
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,840
