00:20:43,320 --> 00:20:44,560
I used to think

290
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,480
it's better that you died.

291
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:50,640
If one wants to be a king,

292
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,920
