00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,840
Even Pengju didn't discern your tricks.

301
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,320
I didn't get rid of

302
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,600
the Nails of Seven Torments,

303
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:22,960
