304
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,120
Pinning one nail into my body

305
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:28,640
every three months.

306
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:31,080
This way, gradually,

307
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:33,920
