00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:49,600
This is unacceptable.

564
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:51,760
You're right.

565
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:54,200
I've failed in teaching my son.

566
00:36:55,160 --> 00:36:57,240
Shame on me.

567
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:16,920
I'm also risking my reputation

568
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:20,480
to take out
these three pieces of Glazed Armor.

569
00:37:23,200 --> 00:37:24,680
I'll be honest with you.

570
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:28,880
If you indeed value our deal,

571
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:32,320
you know what to do.

572
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,200
I know what you mean.

573
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:39,400
But Mr. Mo,

574
00:37:40,160 --> 00:37:42,320
my son means a lot to me.

575
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:45,080
I'm counting on him
to take care of many things.

576
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,320
How about this?

577
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:50,520
I always keep my promises.

578
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:52,720
I'll double the pay.

579
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:55,240
I will make you satisfied--

580
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:58,440
Today, because of your son,

581
00:37:58,520 --> 00:38:00,400
everybody knows

582
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:02,160
I'm working with you, Scorpion King,

583
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:04,160
and the Ghost Valley.

584
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:06,920
How can I instruct my disciples
after this?

585
00:38:23,160 --> 00:38:24,160
I got it.

586
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:28,280
When things are done,

587
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:34,840
I'll offer my son's head

588
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:38,280
as an apology.

589
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:04,080
Traitor, what did you do to the prince?

590
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:07,960
Zhou Zishu.

591
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,720
He treated you so well.

592
00:39:13,520 --> 00:39:15,760
Even now, he didn't want to kill you.

593
00:39:17,040 --> 00:39:18,800
But you didn't show any gratitude.

594
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:21,880
The internal injury he has

595
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:24,800
is caused by a unique skill of my sect,

596
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:27,280
which is Freezing Aroma Palm.

597
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:30,880
His heart meridians got hurt badly.

598
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:34,680
He has to lie in bed
for the rest of his life.

599
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:37,440
Only my sect's martial arts can fix him.

600
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:39,760
But there is only one man left

601
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:42,280
who knows how to do it.

602
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,280
Guess who he is?

603
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:46,400
Stop the nonsense!

604
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:49,680
What do you want in exchange
for saving the prince?

605
00:39:50,520 --> 00:39:51,640
Spit it out!

606
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:58,040
Pengju.

607
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,360
Did you think

608
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,520
I only hit him with my palm

609
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:05,760
because I went easy on him?

610
00:40:08,680 --> 00:40:10,120
I'm so sad

611
00:40:11,520 --> 00:40:13,520
that you know nothing about me

612
00:40:15,520 --> 00:40:17,840
even after working for me
for so many years.

613
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,400
Zhou Zishu.

614
00:40:28,680 --> 00:40:31,440
You can't threaten the prince this way.

615
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,200
If you do not cure him,

616
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:35,360
other highly-skilled doctors can.

617
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:41,400
I will risk my life

618
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:45,720
to beg him to put you to death

619
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:47,360
and cut you into pieces.

620
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:49,720
Pengju.

621
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,960
You are really scaring me.

622
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,160
Kill me.

623
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,120
Kill me.

624
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:58,000
Then he will die as well.

625
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:00,040
At worst,

626
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:02,200
I will die first

627
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:05,000
and wait for him in the netherworld.

628
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:06,000
You--

629
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,040
Shame on you!

630
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:12,600
You don't think

631
00:41:13,160 --> 00:41:14,960
I ran the Window of Heaven

632
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:17,800
with my integrity, do you?

633
00:41:23,240 --> 00:41:24,240
Great.

634
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:26,360
Great!

635
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:30,240
Lord Zhou, we'll see.

636
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,760
Let's see who can outlast the other.

637
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:35,880
All right.

638
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:37,800
Let's do that.

639
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:40,280
After all,

640
00:41:41,120 --> 00:41:42,680
I can't live long.

641
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:45,600
I won't lose anything either way.

